Offers.name: Nail Trims (Sunnyvale)
Offers.description: Nail Trims and Scent Gland Cleanings the first Saturday of every month at For Other Living Things in Sunnyvale.

Offers.name: Home Health Checks (Sunnyvale)
Offers.description:
Home Health Check demonstrations teach you how to make sure your rabbit is healthy and how to spot if something may be wrong. You will be given a handout to take home with you for reference. If you would also like your rabbit's nails trimmed, please book that separately. 

This is for Home Health Checks on Saturdays at For Other Living Things in Sunnyvale.

Offers.name: Rabbit Haven Bunny Hop Event (San Jose)
Offers.description:
This is a safe indoor space for your spayed/neutered bunnies to play and meet other bunnies! Admission is $8.00 per bunny. Fun for everyone and everybun! 

Please see www.therabbithaven.org for specific event dates.

Pet Food Express:  1152 Blossom Hill Road, San Jose, CA
